{
  "stem": "8947.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now under this conditions, the way you were, you get into the barracks-- you want to hear how my barracks look?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want to have the story?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, in-- when I got to Auschwitz, the-- the great-- I could have gotten a worse time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In 1944, the greatest Jewish extermination was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people came, you know-- Jewish people were transported from all over Europe, and from the different countries occupied by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they did not have any more, nothing in the barrack, nothing when I came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had no more wooden planks, you know, no more beds, nothing, just the barren floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the barrack was big, it could accommodate 500 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were two entrances, and there was a door in the middle, a separating door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, you know, this barrack couldn't normally accommodate 500 people, but they made it accommodate, because we were like sardines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, at night you had to push up your feet and-- and you'd be in a fetal position, because everyone was, you know, next to each other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And not to speak of, they was very poorly made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when it was raining the rain came into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were given pails, you know, to push out the rain from the barracks, to actually take out the rain with pails from the barracks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was-- there was an incident that I will talk to you about, which I will never forget in the barrack I was.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were in the barrack through the night and I had dreams that I was home, and I was combing my hair.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then suddenly, pitch dark in there, and it's cold in those parts of Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
